      <dc:title>Typewritten postcard from Rinn to Schenker, dated December 5, [1930]</dc:title>
      <dcterms:created>1930-12-05T12:00:00Z</dcterms:created>
      <dcterms:dateSubmitted>2018-02-22</dcterms:dateSubmitted>
      <dc:description>Rinn has extracted "aphorisms" from the three Meisterwerk volumes and sent the
        page-proofs to Otto Vrieslander. — He would like to see the Tonwille pamphlets, with a view
        to reprinting some of its articles.</dc:description>
      <dc:subject>technisch; technical; Arbeit; work; Aphorismenschatz; store of aphorisms; Auswahl;
        selection; Umbruchexemplar; copy of page-proofs; Besprechung; review; Heft; issue;
        Inhaltsverzeichnis; table of contents</dc:subject>


